dc_title_s: Address Points City of Madison, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2020. [The points in this layer are the general locations of current address data in the City of Madison's property system. They are placed automatically at the center of the tax parcel that the address is associated with. They do not reflect the actual location of the address as represented by a building access location or front door.MAILCODE field values:A = Residential addressC= Commercial address]
uw_supplemental_s: Archived dataset at UW-Madison. For the most current version of this data please visit: https://data-cityofmadison.opendata.arcgis.com/
